Description: AI-powered terminal assistant for Ubuntu
 AI Terminal Assistant converts natural language requests into safe
 Ubuntu shell commands using OpenAI's GPT models. Features include:
 .
  * Natural language to shell command conversion
  * Built-in security validation
  * Interactive and single-command modes
  * System-wide installation and configuration
  * Comprehensive logging and audit trails
 .
 The assistant helps users execute complex shell operations without
 needing to remember exact command syntax.